# Installation Windows



### Step 1:

On google type "mySQL windows" or go to this link:

* [https://dev.mysql.com/downloads/windows/installer/5.7.html](https://dev.mysql.com/downloads/windows/installer/5.7.html) 
* Download and install web community 

### Step 2:

```text
cd %HOMEPATH%

mkdir Documents\workspace microting

cd Documents\workspace\microting

git clone https://github.com/microting/eform-angular-frontend.git
```

### Step 3:

Download and install node.JS Windows installer [https://nodejs.org/en/download/](https://nodejs.org/en/download/) 

![](data:image/png;base64,)

### Step 4:

```text
cd %HOMEPATH%

cd Documents\workspace\microting\eform-angular-frontend\eform-client

npm install
```

### Step 5:

Download install .Net core SDK for WINDOWS 

![](data:image/png;base64,)

### Step 6:

```text
cd %HOMEPATH%

cd Documents\workspace\microting\eform-angular-frontend\eFormAPI

dotnet run --project eFormAPI.Web\eFormAPI.Web.csproj
```

### Step 7:

```text
cd %HOMEPATH%

cd Documents\workspace\microting\eform-angular-frontend\eform-client

npm start
```
